it's fine with me.

308
00:21:31,830 --> 00:21:33,830
I wouldn't be so sure.

309
00:21:34,200 --> 00:21:35,330
You!

310
00:21:35,460 --> 00:21:38,330
Rossiu has turned his back
on humanity.

311
00:21:41,300 --> 00:21:46,420
When the moon hits, they will be swallowed,
shelters and all, by the Earth's crust,

312
00:21:46,510 --> 00:21:48,130
